title: SPY Presents: Win The Shades Ken Wore During The Filming of Gymkhana FOUR!
description: Win the SPY + Ken Block Gymkhana Limited Edition Murena sunglasses signed and worn by Ken during Gymkhana FOUR! One grand prize winner will receive the autographed shades; three runners-up will receive a pair of the sunglasses (sans signature, but rare nonetheless)! Post "Gymkhana FOUR" on the SPY Facebook wall, to enter to win on Wednesday, August 24 at 2 p.m. PST.
